      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://mungops.github.io/devops/terraform/terraform07/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ &lt;strong&gt;Terraform으로 EC2, VPC, RDS, Kubernetes 클러스터 생성&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-terraform으로-ec2-vpc-rds-kubernetes-클러스터-생성&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-terraform%ec%9c%bc%eb%a1%9c-ec2-vpc-rds-kubernetes-%ed%81%b4%eb%9f%ac%ec%8a%a4%ed%84%b0-%ec%83%9d%ec%84%b1&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1 &lt;strong&gt;EC2 인스턴스 생성 예제&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-ec2-인스턴스-생성-예제&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-ec2-%ec%9d%b8%ec%8a%a4%ed%84%b4%ec%8a%a4-%ec%83%9d%ec%84%b1-%ec%98%88%ec%a0%9c&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-hcl&#34; data-lang=&#34;hcl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;provider&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;aws&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;  region&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;ap-northeast-2&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;resource&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;aws_instance&amp;#34; &amp;#34;web&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; {&#